text: José Gabriel dos Santos Silva (born 21 January 1999), known as Zé Gabriel, is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Internacional. ==Professional career== Zé Gabriel is a youth international of Corinthians, and moved to Internacional in 2019. Zé Gabriel made his professional debut with Internacional in a 2-1 Campeonato Brasileiro Série A loss to Fluminense FC on 3 August 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * Internacional Profile Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sergipe Category:Brazilian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Sport Club Internacional players Category:Campeonato Brasileiro Série A players
